score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"所以應該用公司錢去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb0a7a7fe513cc2f8f1e8e790dfd915e4c608de","tid":836122,"uid":148601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"樓主有無去過旅行？<br />\n同朋友去個種開心同難忘<br />\n依家幾年都仲好記得"},{"pid":"48a7f20dc3fabe5dd0beee9b26452f727750ed00","tid":836122,"uid":15895,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"笑左<br />\n樓主加油，其實香港好大，衣食住行樣樣齊，唔洗出國啦。<br />\n利申：grad左去完3個月歐洲番黎，洗鳩哂d錢，第時老左肯定唔夠錢洗餓死"},{"pid":"783c11bdf42b591e57d25ef63034eceae51f614e","tid":836122,"uid":8040,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"以前我都有一排好似你咁諗<br />\n但自從去過一次旅行就唔再係咁諗<br />\n<br />\n講真，同成班朋友去旅行得讀書時間做到<br />\n大家一齊sem break 放暑假一齊去，非常容易就時間<br />\n<br />\n到出來做野，就唔再容易夾時間，因為大家假期唔多，同得女朋友去就同唔到朋友去<br />\n<br />\n去到30歲，大家開始有家庭，就寧願同老婆仔女去旅行都唔再會同朋友去<br />\n<br />\n我都好後悔當年無同朋友去歐遊,而家淨係夾到期去下4-5 日台灣日本泡菜短trip<br />\n食大餐隨時都食到啦，儲錢出來做野之後就會覺得part time 嗰啲跟本唔係咩一回事"},{"pid":"137dc02d1c3348b67aad3edab2e559e4e4257d53","tid":836122,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"用自己錢買樓都好on9"},{"pid":"0ca30959d5e1f7cb5056c5243a1a48af0fc10afa","tid":836122,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb0a7a7fe513cc2f8f1e8e790dfd915e4c608de","tid":836122,"uid":148601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"樓主有無去過旅行？<br />\n同朋友去個種開心同難忘<br />\n依家幾年都仲好記得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"我老母30年前同佢朋友去左幾次中國旅行<br />\n佢而家得閒都仲講緊當年經歷<br />\n<br />\n跟本去旅行無論開心定唔開心都可以記成世"},{"pid":"87d3f4a621a0d646e9137685b22d8e8e4c614552","tid":836122,"uid":165421,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:51:27.000Z","msg":"我都覺得樓豬好on9<br />\n一開post就攻擊人唔識理財今朝有酒今朝醉<br />\n自己錢夠去旅行嘅人本來就已經撇除左停手停口嗰批，翻工唔係必要<br />\n你留喺香港食好西都一樣係拎啲人工去消遣<br />\n但去一次旅行嘅充實感為我嚟講大過食10幾餐高級菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋有啲風景名勝你留翻廿年後去又係另一番景象，甚至好似大堡礁咁可能收咗皮<br />\n利申: 如果唔係唔想用屋企錢自己去旅行都唔會番pt"},{"pid":"4300c89bfbdd84bb1222dd308accb7f84a5ea4e2","tid":836122,"uid":38914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"137dc02d1c3348b67aad3edab2e559e4e4257d53","tid":836122,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:47:23.000Z","msg":"用自己錢買樓都好on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:53:56.000Z","msg":"完美說法"},{"pid":"fabf0b4926491bc710b6bcba9c26b1d4dda7046a","tid":836122,"uid":144063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:55:30.000Z","msg":"香港食壽司成千蚊<br />\n都未必夠日本300蚊好食 正宗 新鮮<br />\n<br />\n香港食拉面 百幾蚊<br />\n日本 70蚊都好正"},{"pid":"8fcfd756944591ec84c9fa81bab8dedd99876cee","tid":836122,"uid":134864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:58:15.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n所以好多女做G俾人包去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e0acec935790e23d554fe0931dac4b701b4d22","tid":836122,"uid":6128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:58:30.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n食野我都覺得好浪費錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e821663802be0bc40d7573e2f811b8c32ce7fc4","tid":836122,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a81182ed7fc2f7e1f64f4df2aa28a9fe20b5f65f","tid":836122,"uid":199252,"like":3,"dislike":32,"score":-29,"quote":{"pid":"3c0b29344ff49bafb77b2613586f2ecf05d0d188","tid":836122,"uid":38914,"like":85,"dislike":2,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:24:02.000Z","msg":"世界咁大 後生冇家庭or經濟負擔其實去睇下世界仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好過你乜都未去過 同人社交傾下計都o哂嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到死個日原來諗返自己為左層樓 乜都未去過 層樓先啱啱好供完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你呢家有氣有力去點都好過退休你有心冇力去丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定還是葡萄人地有得去 自己冇朋友陪所以冇得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:26:24.000Z","msg":"宜家睇下世界將來瞓街vs宜家o嘴將來有安穩生活 <br />\n我揀後者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦你 屌你老母"},{"pid":"6c34fcc75062a372b6ec70fef813fd8e6706296b","tid":836122,"uid":144063,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"去台北 8蚊一碗魯肉飯又平又好食<br />\n10蚊一杯珍珠奶茶 <br />\n早餐蛋餅又平 <br />\n<br />\n泰國果d地方洗費又平香港勁多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依到已經賺左<br />\n<br />\n仲未計去旅行果種開心"},{"pid":"f8c0a36cb7baf265e930e2c1cc042f83d81a6533","tid":836122,"uid":103514,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a3f1248391b8577e7b12ec9724961fb4c9566fff","tid":836122,"uid":199252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"淨係機票已經幾千，仲要買呢樣買嗰樣，我唔明點解d大學生肯將辛苦part time儲落ge錢一次過fing哂<br />\n我寧願食幾餐大餐或者就咁儲起佢都唔會揀去旅行<br />\n如果你儲到錢你會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似我咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去旅行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"//我寧願食幾餐大餐或者就咁儲起佢都唔會揀去旅行//<br />\n<br />\n我覺得食大餐仲on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旅行起碼都可以增長見聞，有多啲回憶<br />\n食野落肚，24個鐘後就變屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n-----------<br />\n睇到我上面咁講係咪即刻想反駁? <br />\n咁你明白點解要尊重人地嘅興趣未<br />\n人地點用自己錢係自己嘅事，話唔定去完旅行返嚟，佢嘅人生路會走得更寬闊。<br />\n反而俾你儲多少少錢，十年後通漲可能連個腸仔包都買唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見你問得出呢啲問題，應該都仲係讀緊書<br />\n過多幾年啦，過多幾年你出嚟做野諗法成熟啲<br />\n你就會後悔自己開過呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44fc3e61ff8f355b7eee832e38be59a4ac7e167f","tid":836122,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"樓主一定冇女朋友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c29d03e1e02f0b1c4857a387d7a6a943a67c05a","tid":836122,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ff64ea0de5535af02364fda59f7c20a4054b977","tid":836122,"uid":199252,"like":7,"dislike":119,"score":-112,"quote":{"pid":"1ef779dd4e1a807f547f08ad0fff0f6a316e5ecc","tid":836122,"uid":53798,"like":66,"dislike":2,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"唔用自己錢咁你點去旅行？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:12:20.000Z","msg":"我意思係作為一個學生，唔應該將咁辛苦賺到的錢係旅行到fing哂，人到中年有安穩生活有多餘錢就去得啫，學生乜都未有就咁揮霍我個人就唔係好buy"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:18:12.000Z","msg":"咁你人到中年仲可唔可以自由自在去旅行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d51bc0b8c9715b3cdf5ec7b7f48c470d8145993","tid":836122,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵完啲錢唔撚洗仲戇鳩啦<br />\n<br />\n明明想去旅行但呃自己唔想去旅行  應該儲起啲錢就仲戇鳩<br />\n<br />\n想去旅行又有錢剩就諗下方法  搵多啲錢   唔係諗辦法死慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"839e051fac033116cd6da43ca0d7e5723067534c","tid":836122,"uid":175402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:30:46.000Z","msg":"錢賺黎就要洗<br />\n咁梗係用係自己鍾意做既野<br />\n儲埋唔用你D錢只係一堆數字<br />\n同埋你估真係唔去旅行就買到樓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ac7d517683fb3dc2432ae218807b431f3a8319","tid":836122,"uid":3912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:35:37.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪以為個個都好似你咁揾幾千蚊個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且一個人使錢多嘅時候先會有動力去揾更多錢返嚟"},{"pid":"f1248f7b387473cd85f4480b03f42ded3927c761","tid":836122,"uid":18899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f006c1e22fe0eb38d24ac2a9c3d6b315101cf608","tid":836122,"uid":8308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:35:51.000Z","msg":"認同 不嬲都係daddy俾錢我去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n樓主又冇錢又懶又唔肯儲錢 淨係識眼紅人地去旅行<br />\n人地有錢做咩關你鬼事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff2d17fed26527f0d50082072ec8bcef51b29af","tid":836122,"uid":149422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"以前都喺咁諗 但去過幾次又會諗 咁辛苦得個幾千蚊   要儲錢之後番工二三個月可能已經係而家一年 不如而家見識多啲 況且實會通賬到時仲貴"},{"pid":"7ba31f23388df271c6ba8b80cb3be264860f0475","tid":836122,"uid":152697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"去個旅行用咩自己錢 屋企人比<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae65f2a513f12b8a2033286fde1f1461b6ae950c","tid":836122,"uid":143670,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:47:29.000Z","msg":"香港地生活太刻板, <br />\n如果年青時可能性最高最大嘅時候<br />\n都唔去睇下試下, 好容易變左做其他人,<br />\n<br />\n唔好睇小附近地方<br />\n音樂/飲食/購物文化差異好大,<br />\n流行曲都可以細分好多流派, 追小說可以係風氣仲有好多會拍成電影, 食野原來可以有好多不同價位分野, 講質地, 手工細緻, 産地係邊區, 買野唔冼講, 選擇性同方法唔同好多, 仲有好成熟嘅二手市場等等等<br />\n<br />\n以上唔係講香港唔好, 其實某方面可能香港比較好,<br />\n重點係要培養個人睇法, 係先要試多啲睇多啲,<br />\n正正係近近地容易去, 先要去多啲<br />\n認識一個地方可以好深入, 而插入點可以好簡單,<br />\n你睇下台式珍珠奶茶係香港咪又係賣到成行成市<br />\n<br />\n唔去睇下點知下一樣興咩?<br />\n係香港地晚晚睇TVB, 快餐剩係得老麥KFC, 正餐剩係得美心, 商場個個一樣樣, 真係開拓唔到眼界<br />\n<br />\n大事小事都好多時源於興趣<br />\n興趣係需要培養, 培養需要好多嘗試<br />\n年輕時敢想敢做就去多啲啦<br />\n一萬幾千唔志在<br />\n<br />\n錢係越搵越多<br />\n好奇心係越老越少<br />\n<br />\n趁後生飛多D的啦"},{"pid":"af837001fe98769634ddc844cf02c61eb0207295","tid":836122,"uid":76735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"去次旅行要洗幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去次台灣都係五六千蚊 去下韓國頂多咪萬零蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個萬零蚊係咪比到你日後安穩既生活？<br />\n同埋你係學生先多時間去旅行咋 出左社會請個假去旅行都要睇人面色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通等到中年退休先去呀？到時你都無精神無體力玩啦"},{"pid":"8105b2f01e00ca6a422808a2917dead564271b0e","tid":836122,"uid":22719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"我幾時都話<br />\n洗唔晒份糧咪有錢淨<br />\n享受係人生其中一種動力驅使你搵錢"},{"pid":"b4eef447f1b682944f93bb5bcbb916b766ddba24","tid":836122,"uid":111253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:56:19.000Z","msg":"樓主是咪未出身？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  到你返第一份工，唔洗三個月就好想去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"530958a137e12d5d09aef183f8d99776cd5a2775","tid":836122,"uid":181804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"負評 原過係比樓主你既"},{"pid":"a67c8341e9a21325813541583e33f2ef28a0c95a","tid":836122,"uid":211878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:00:54.000Z","msg":"拎綜援去旅行好精明"},{"pid":"58299f66a1d33fcd88504ec3872b0cf7b2a9d129","tid":836122,"uid":203889,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3e285091a3741ac3f9fbf529b309992d630aeb17","tid":836122,"uid":199252,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"其實我問得唔係太好，我意思係唔明白點解d學生願意將辛苦做幾個月兼職賺到的錢係短時間內去旅行用哂，得嗰一星期的快樂，我覺得唔值"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:14:15.000Z","msg":"因為其實學生時代先係最有閒錢玩，無乜責任要負擔，賺既可以使晒佢唔使左計右計<br />\n出到黎做野就要俾家用同生活費同還loan，更加無錢剩，朋友個個返工去約去旅行都未必約到<br />\n<br />\n同埋其實做一年part time辛辛苦苦儲到果幾皮野，你出到黎返工就會知有幾少<br />\n少到你趁grad trip用左大部分都唔會對你未來造成太大影響"},{"pid":"ed530fe7ba9fe8ff6b82781c02c6224543b1ea64","tid":836122,"uid":108022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:14:38.000Z","msg":"個世界好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目光放長遠D，去旅行都係擴