 src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 萬幾蚊 畢業正常返工一兩個禮拜就有啦 慳埋啲咁嘅數 慘"},{"pid":"ee6934edf3e366bf44d7055b74eaea18e61f04a8","tid":836122,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝大家珍貴的意見，屌醒我呢個大學fm<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有你嘅道理嘅不過大家河水不犯井水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d2a75f9beb3439a145fdde057417e9e0194bfd","tid":836122,"uid":184932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:54:49.000Z","msg":"唔係偷唔係搶<br />\n你理得人點揀"},{"pid":"7509546ba40eeed3003a776ae02cf4dd93275682","tid":836122,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T16:58:04.000Z","msg":"樓豬用開女人錢去旅行又食又拎咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd1168a11e2838d4e3bbe8dc620931fb4f91545","tid":836122,"uid":833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"以前細個每年暑假屋企人都會帶我去旅行，都係東南亞為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果陣雖然對錢冇咩概念，但都會諗去得幾日，一家幾口就冇左幾萬蚊，點解唔儲起佢好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直到依家出黎做野終於知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  直頭唔想返工淨係去旅行<br />\n<br />\n爸媽多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7034ec784842c8327ae20fc6a09f1103c5e16f37","tid":836122,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:04:06.000Z","msg":"劉嗚偉?"},{"pid":"fab201335d4b621f65c76e38e0788cb16f371e1a","tid":836122,"uid":139652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6741e8d5c2e452da493287119059d8c62b622a07","tid":836122,"uid":199252,"like":19,"dislike":86,"score":-67,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:09:20.000Z","msg":"你地唔會覺得好唔扺咩？一個短trip就無哂part time賺的所有錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:10:16.000Z","msg":"覺 但係好值得 做人都係求開心姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433fecf4c6e6621c781c644eac703a9e09b58745","tid":836122,"uid":18411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"都唔明你咁執著做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都係鍾意儲錢既，少去旅行，連食好嘢都少<br />\n咁我班同學都唔少人得閒就周圍去<br />\n大家選擇唔同姐，無話邊個威D"},{"pid":"c7d9d475bf8af191bc5dcf3b3913be15bcde521e","tid":836122,"uid":102542,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"有錢使乜理旅行使幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：早排去左東京兩日，連酒店/機票使左18000<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab90f5469135490f754a3cd18310a51dfe5824a","tid":836122,"uid":63342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:19:15.000Z","msg":"後生同中年去嘅分別就係個心態 <br />\n比著你3,40歲重會唔會去skydiving ?"},{"pid":"7e79133c87e396676b41016ac5bf24ae78cc70d6","tid":836122,"uid":191572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:20:02.000Z","msg":"用人地錢去旅行咪得囉"},{"pid":"e36c54fc6ee9621c146039edd68541ccb6355e80","tid":836122,"uid":11973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb0a7a7fe513cc2f8f1e8e790dfd915e4c608de","tid":836122,"uid":148601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T14:37:31.000Z","msg":"樓主有無去過旅行？<br />\n同朋友去個種開心同難忘<br />\n依家幾年都仲好記得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:21:40.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錢 去完旅行可以再揾過<br />\n但後生時未有家庭負擔可以同班老死一齊衝出香港去玩去癲嗰種興奮喜悅真係幾多錢都買唔到<br />\n玩完返嚟分享回味再一齊plan下次幾時再去<br />\n個感覺真係好正好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔明點解樓主諗嘢咁怪<br />\n未試過同fd去旅行嘅咩?<br />\n係咪冇fd同你去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係見到人哋一大班fd有男有女咁去玩得開心<br />\n自己冇人陪你去就嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑人哋唔識理財<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定還是自己毒遊完post相上fb/ig點知冇人like就唔憤氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以覺得攞舊錢食咗佢好過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f39feffcb363d7628b4a71a82a427d08fb649e","tid":836122,"uid":16451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"唔去下旅行搵番黎d錢邊食得哂<br />\n緊係去埋旅行洗埋佢"},{"pid":"fba2fefbbcdefa2219f7b0bacc57f2fa5a7afacb","tid":836122,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:25:20.000Z","msg":"仲以為樓主想叫人幫佢運木雕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18fe7cef510d9228e16a1711e9b5d652c0593a2","tid":836122,"uid":12013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44fc3e61ff8f355b7eee832e38be59a4ac7e167f","tid":836122,"uid":45290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T15:17:27.000Z","msg":"樓主一定冇女朋友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T17:30:30.000Z","msg":"應該連朋友都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}